OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAcute drought leaves France
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fshort of drinking water    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The French government has set up a     
OL,6, crisis team to tackle a historic       
OL,7, drought that has left more than 100    
OL,8, municipalities short of drinking water.
OL,10,FTrucks are taking water to those areas,
OL,11,Fas "there is nothing left in the       
OL,12,Fpipes", Minister for Ecological        
OL,13,FTransition Christophe Bechu said.      
OL,15,FThe prime minister's office said it was
OL,16,FFrance's worst recorded drought. Water 
OL,17,Fuse is being restricted in 93 regions. 
OL,19,FDry conditions are expected to continue
OL,20,Ffor at least the next two weeks.       
